cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.AI, cs.DC, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with distributed control synthesis, which is a subfield of control theory. Therefore, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses decision-making and communication, which are topics related to multi-agent systems, making cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) another likely category. The paper also mentions using local decisions over joint decisions, which involves some level of artificial intelligence, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a possible category. The paper also deals with distributed computing, which is related to cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). Finally, the paper mentions minimizing communication, which is related to machine learning and optimization, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) a possible category as well.
